item.title: CVE-2020-6262|2024-08-04T08:55:22.163Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20application%20server%20abap%20%28st-pi%29
item.description: Service Data Download in SAP Application Server ABAP (ST-PI, before versions 2008_1_46C, 2008_1_620, 2008_1_640, 2008_1_700, 2008_1_710, 740) allows an attacker to inject code that can be executed by the application. An attacker could thereby control the behavior of the application and the whole ABAP system leading to Code Injection.
